<li><a href="http://store.wherethehellismatt.com/" target="_blank">Offizieller Shop: Download, Soundtrack, T-Shirts</a></li>
<li><a href="http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/trip-light-feat.-alicia-lemke/id535287301?i=535287402" target="_blank">Soundtrack: Trip The Light bei iTunes</a> &#8211; <a href="http://www.alicialemke.com/" target="_blank">Vocals von Alicia Lemke</a></li>
